ming (HTML, JavaScript, CSS, AJAX)</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n						<td>Web site &amp; Software Development Support</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,3,3,'und',0,'<p><span class=\"textheader01\">Experience by Design provides a range of services to corporate, association, non-profit, and public sector clients looking to offer user-friendly, productive and engaging experiences to users via their web sites or software products. We offer flexible solutions, ranging from one-time consultations to full-scale design and project support. This allows us to align our services and tailor our work to your specific needs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our project portfolio includes software, corporate web sites and intranets, online community and e-commerce web sites, and industry portals for clients in a range of industry sectors; including advocacy, banking, biotech, education, financial services, government, healthcare, housing, media &amp; entertainment, network management, sports, social media, software, technology, telecommunications and wireless. A representative list of our project work includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>AARP</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>AOL</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>American Bankers Association</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"project/afp\">Association for Financial Professionals (AFP) </a></td>\r\n			<td class=\"case-study\"><a href=\"projects/afp\"><img src=\"http://experience.vgmediagroup.com/sites/default/files/casestudy.gif\" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"project/brabeion\">Brabeion Software (a division of EMC Corporation) </a></td>\r\n			<td class=\"case-study\"><a href=\"projects/brabeion\"><img src=\"http://experience.vgmediagroup.com/sites/default/fi