gramming (HTML, JavaScript, CSS, AJAX)</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n						<td>Web site &amp; Software Development Support</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,3,3,'und',0,'<p><span class=\"textheader01\">Experience by Design provides a range of services to corporate, association, non-profit, and public sector clients looking to offer user-friendly, productive and engaging experiences to users via their web sites or software products. We offer flexible solutions, ranging from one-time consultations to full-scale design and project support. This allows us to align our services and tailor our work to your specific needs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our project portfolio includes software, corporate web sites and intranets, online community and e-commerce web sites, and industry portals for clients in a range of industry sectors; including advocacy, banking, biotech, education, financial services, government, healthcare, housing, media &amp; entertainment, network management, sports, social media, software, technology, telecommunications and wireless. A representative list of our project work includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>AARP</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>AOL</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>American Bankers Association</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"project/afp\">Association for Financial Professionals (AFP) </a></td>\r\n			<td class=\"case-study\"><a href=\"projects/afp\"><img src=\"http://experience.vgmediagroup.com/sites/default/files/casestudy.gif\" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"project/brabeion\">Brabeion Software (a division of EMC Corporation) </a></td>\r\n			<td class=\"case-study\"><a href=\"projects/brabeion\"><img src=\"http://experience.vgmediagroup.com/sites/default/files/casestudy.gif\" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Bradford Networks</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>BuildTopia</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Celera</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>DEWalt Industrial Tool Company</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"project/brabeion\">Enumerate</a></td>\r\n			<td class=\"case-study\"><a href=\"projects/enumerate\"><img src=\"http://experience.vgmediagroup.com/sites/default/files/casestudy.gif\" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fannie Mae</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>FINRA</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Freddie Mac</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Genius Rocket</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Georgetown University Medical Center</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"project/brabeion\">GoalFace </a></td>\r\n			<td class=\"case-study\"><a href=\"projects/goalface\"><img src=\"http://experience.vgmediagroup.com/sites/default/files/casestudy.gif\" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Humane Society of the United States</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"project/knowledgeplex\">Knowledgeplex</a></td>\r\n			<td class=\"case-study\"><a href=\"projects/knowledgeplex\"><img src=\"http://experience.vgmediagroup.com/sites/default/files/casestudy.gif\" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Lockheed Martin</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Military Officers Association of America</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Perfman</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>SabiaMed</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Sallie Mae</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"project/sprint\">Sprint (formerly Nextel Communications)</a></td>\r\n			<td class=\"case-study\"><a href=\"projects/sprint\"><img src=\"http://experience.vgmediagroup.com/sites/default/files/casestudy.gif\" /></a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Sprint (formerly Nextel Communications)</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Teleglobe (a division of Tata Communications)</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>US Department of Transportation</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>US Food &amp; Drug Administration</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Verizon</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>VisualCV</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','page',0,4,4,'und',0,'<p class=\"textheader01\">Experience by Design has been designing successful user experiences for over a decade.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text01\">Experience by Design brings a holistic and proven approach to the planning and design of user-friendly web sites and software products. Our methodology centers on the guiding principle that business goals and user needs must be understood, and carefully balanced, for technology to be delivered in engaging, meaningful and effective ways.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text01\">Together with <a href=\"services\">our services</a>, our approach ensures a project\'s integrity through the entire development cycle-from initial discovery, on to design, and through successful launch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"text01\"><b>How will the project be managed?</b><br />\r\nOur methodology provides an approach to planning and designing web sites and software products that balance user needs and a client’s business goals and technical capabilities.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr align=\"center\">\r\n			<td><img height=\"189\" src=\"sites/default/files/diagram01_sm.gif\" width=\"461\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"right\"><img height=\"7\" src=\"sites/default/files/arrow_sm.gif\" style=\"padding-right:5px;\" width=\"7\" /><a class=\"colorbox link_callout\" href=\"sites/default/files/diagram01_lg.gif\" target=\"_blank\">Enlarge Image</a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text01\">Our methodology is inclusive and accessible to all project stakeholders-business, technical and others. Our approach gets teams from initial discovery to design and development in a focused, structured and efficient manner, resulting in projects that launch on time, on strategy and on budget.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"text01\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"4\"><b>Our methodology consists of the following four (4) phases:</b></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\"><img height=\"8\" src=\"sites/deafult/files/spacer.gif\" width=\"1\" /></td>\r\n			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">\r\n			<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"8\">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n						<td><a class=\"text01\" href=\"methodology/discovery\">Discovery</a></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n						<td><a class=\"text01\" href=\"methodology/analysis\">Analysis &amp; Modeling</a></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n						<td><a class=\"text01\" href=\"methodology/specification\">Design &amp; Specification</a></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n						<td><a class=\"text01\" href=\"methodology/development\">Development &amp; Integration</a></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','page',0,5,5,'und',0,'<p class=\"textheader01\">What are your strategic goals? Who is your target audience? What information and functionality must your web site or software provide to be successful? What other factors are likely to influence the success of your web site or software product?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During Discovery we work with your team to answer these and other questions to ensure goals, objectives and priorities for the project are defined and rightly aligned before kicking off <a class=\"text01\" href=\"analysis\">the Analysis and Concept Modeling phase</a>.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,6,6,'und',0,'<p class=\"textheader01\">How will users locate and get to the information they want or need? How should content be organized? What information should be placed front and center? What functionality will be available and where?</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text01\">During Analysis and Modeling we take a closer look at business goals, audience needs, content assets, technology platforms and other factors that influence design decisions. Using the findings from <a class=\"text01\" href=\"discovery\">Discovery phase</a>, we work with you in a series of collaborative sessions — each intended to facilitate discussion and build consensus as the team works to refine ideas and requirements. The results are concept models and mockups that identify how information will be organized and what features and functionality are required to meet user needs and achieve the desired goals. All assumptions and requirements from this phase of the project are gathered and documented in the appropriate format (e.g. reports and diagrams) for review and approval before <a class=\"text01\" href=\"specification\">the Design and Specification phase</a> begins.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,7,7,'und',0,'<p class=\"textheader01\">What will the site look like? How will content display? How will the functional and interactive components work?</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text01\">Concepts created during <a class=\"text01\" href=\"analysis\">the Analysis and Modeling phase</a> are refined into final designs and specifications. How information will display on each page and the ways that navigation and interactive features will work are all defined in detail during design and specification. The documents created to capture the design and specifications serve as blueprints to guide the visual designers responsible for the look and feel of the user interface, as well as the teams performing the build and testing functions during <a class=\"text01\" href=\"development\">the Development and Integration phase</a>.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,8,8,'und',0,'<p class=\"textheader01\">Marshalling the people and resources needed for the build, testing and a successful launch is a complex set of tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text01\">Our role during Development and Integration is to ensure the site or software product is built according to plans set during <a class=\"text01\" href=\"specification\"> the Design and Specification phase</a>. We participate in the review, user-acceptance testing and resolution of issues that emerge during development. We work to address these issues in ways that conform to the established design strategy and patterns, and help ensure that the potential negative impacts of changes to the user experience are understood and minimized.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','webform',0,22,22,'und',0,'<p><span class=\"textheader01\">How does your Web site measure up?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img height=\"20\" src=\"http://www.experiencebydesign.com/images/spacer.gif\" width=\"1\" />Experience by Design can provide an evaluation of your Web site to help you gauge the quality of experience it provides to those who visit and use it. Our Site Reviews are performed by knowledgeable user experience professionals. They provide an objective evaluation of your Web site based on a review of key usability and user experience criteria. The Site Review identifies issues that negatively impact your site\'s performance and use. To get started, please answer the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"ast\">* indicates required fields</span></p>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','webform',0,23,23,'und',0,'<p class=\"text01\">Send us a message by filling in all fields in the form below, or by sending<br />\r\nan e-mail to <a href=\"http://www.experiencebydesign.com/contact.html#experiencebydesign.com\" id=\"contact\">contact at experiencebydesign dot com </a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"textcallout\"><span class=\"text01bold\">Phone:</span><br />\r\n<span class=\"text06_callout\">240.752.1010 </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"textcallout\"><span class=\"text01bold\">Address:</span><br />\r\n10319 Westlake Drive, #101<br />\r\nBethesda, MD<br />\r\n20817</span></p>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','project',0,24,24,'und',0,'<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_C\" width=\"100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"textheader01\">Building a daily resource for treasury and finance professionals worldwide. </span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">Overview</span><br />\r\n			The Association for Financial Professionals (AFP) is a membership organization serving 16,000 treasury and finance professionals around the world. AFP provides members with breaking news, economic research and information to keep current in the evolving world of global treasury and finance. AFP also provides members with professional networking, development and training opportunities, as well as public policy representation to legislators and industry regulators.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"center\">\r\n			<table>\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><img src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/AFP.jpg\" /></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Challenge</span><br />\r\n			AFP\'s leadership team wanted to bring their web site inline with the dynamic and rapidly evolving needs of its members in the global finance industry. AFP needed a firm to develop a strategy and plan for a web site that could support the organization\'s strategic plans. Experience by Design was hired to reorganize the web site\'s content, update its look and feel, and upgrade features and functionality as needed to make the site timely, accessible and inline with AFP\'s goals to increase revenue and serve as a daily resource for finance professionals worldwide.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Solution</span><br />\r\n			Experience by Design brought a holistic approach to the strategy for the AFP web site redesign. Experience by Design worked with AFP executives, the project team and stakeholders across the organization to define the target audience, strategic goals and business priorities driving the redesign. Experience by Design also reviewed the organization\'s existing web sites, content assets, strategic plan, competitors and technology platforms to inform the strategy and redesign of the of web site\'s structure, look and feel, page layout, features and functionality; including the AFP store, conference registration and member sign up and renewal. Deliverables included a site map, functional flows, wireframes, a visual style guide and other work products to inform the design, direct development and support testing during the web site implementation.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span class=\"textheader01\">The Result</span><br />\r\n			<span class=\"text01\">Association for Financial Professionals has a web site that is well integrated, more engaging, relevant and aligned to the organization\'s business and strategic goals, as well as the needs of treasury and finance professionals around the world. </span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_E\" width=\"\">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td>\r\n						<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Services</b></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n									<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"100%\">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Audience Profiling</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Competitive Site Analysis</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Concept Modeling</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Content Strategy</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Information Architecture &amp; Navigation Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Interaction &amp; Interface Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Graphic Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Front-end Engineering and Development</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><img height=\"10\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/spacer.gif\" /></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Technologies</b></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n									<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"\">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>CSS</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>JavaScript</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>PHP</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','project',0,25,25,'und',0,'<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_C\" width=\"100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"textheader01\">Strategy and design services for an interactive sports information and online community experience. </span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">Overview</span><br />\r\n			GoalFace (<a href=\"http://www.experiencebydesign.com/www.goalface.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.goalface.com</a>) is a content rich, social media web site for soccer fans, professionals and industry stakeholders that make up the global soccer community. GoalFace brings together a mix of web 2.0 features and content covering 100,000+ soccer players and teams from 200+ professional leagues across Europe, the Americas, Africa and Asia in an engaging, easy-to-use and fun experience.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"center\">\r\n			<table>\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><img src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/GoalFace.jpg\" /></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Challenge</span><br />\r\n			The GoalFace management team needed a firm to help ideate, design and plan a web site with social networking capabilities built around a library of soccer content. They wanted a firm with the ability to create a scalable, unified information architecture that was also versed in the latest web 2.0 and social media trends for a web site expected to be 1,000,000+ pages at launch.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Solution</span><br />\r\n			Experience by Design brought its grounding in information architecture, user experience design and knowledge of online community and social media to help the GoalFace management team document their vision and strategy. Experience by Design worked with the GoalFace team to create a product roadmap to guide the planning, design, build and launch of the web site, widgets and mobile applications to be released in phases over several years. Experience by Design used the strategy and roadmap as inputs to inform the initial concepts and designs for the first version of the GoalFace platform. Work products and deliverables included a site map, navigation models, experience flows and concept wireframes to iterate and advance the design of the web site\'s structure, features, content display, core interactions and user interface patterns. Once approved, Experience by Design developed user interface specifications to guide the teams that built and tested the GoalFace web site and applications.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span class=\"textheader01\">The Result</span><br />\r\n			<span class=\"text01\">GoalFace has a fully integrated web site, along with a strategy and roadmap for an extended suite of content and social media platforms to build out as they work to engage the global soccer community around the passion of the game. </span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_E\" width=\"\">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td>\r\n						<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Services</b></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n									<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"100%\">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Product Ideation &amp; Strategy</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Online Community &amp; Social Media Strategy</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Information Architecture &amp; Navigation Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Task Analysis &amp; Interaction Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>User Experience Modeling</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>User Interface Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Expert Review &amp; User Testing</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Front-end Engineering and Development</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><img height=\"10\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/spacer.gif\" /></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Technologies</b></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n						<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n									<td>CSS</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n									<td>JavaScript</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n									<td>PHP</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n									<td>Objective-C</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','project',0,26,26,'und',0,'<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_C\" width=\"100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"textheader01\">Grew the adoption and use of an industry portal by improving user experience and content relevancy. </span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">Overview</span><br />\r\n			KnowledgePlex is an online news, tools and information resource for the affordable housing and community development field created by Fannie Mae Foundation. Fannie Mae Foundation is a non-profit organization supporting high-performance community organizations and partnering with others to organize, make available and direct the resources needed to facilitate its affordable housing and community revitalization mission.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"center\">\r\n			<table>\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><img src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/cs02_image.gif\" /></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Challenge</span><br />\r\n			KnowledgePlex was created to be the centerpiece of the Fannie Mae Foundation\'s knowledge-sharing programs, as a platform for the affordable housing and community development field to connect, collaborate, share and learn. Fannie Mae Foundation\'s leadership team needed a more refined picture of the KnowledgePlex target audience to guide the redesign of the site and align it more directly with the goals and needs of the target audience.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Solution</span><br />\r\n			Experience by Design was hired to research and build a detailed picture of the target audience for KnowledgePlex that outlined the web site’s audience as well as their goals, wants and needs. Experience by Design used its Audience Discovery™ methodology to manage the project from inception through delivery. Project goals were defined through research and working sessions with internal and external stakeholders. Topics included the makeup, capacity, goals and needs of the various segments within the affordable housing and community development field. Experience by Design conducted interviews, working sessions and focus groups with a representative sample from each of the target segments, and delivered findings and recommendations in a series of deliverables that included an audience profile, personas for the primary targets and a findings report.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span class=\"textheader01\">The Result</span><br />\r\n			<span class=\"text01\">Fannie Mae Foundation has a detailed and refined understanding of their target audience. This understanding supported the successful redesign and alignment of KnowledgePlex’s core features and content to the needs of affordable housing and community development professionals. It has also fostered successful outreach and increased adoption and use of the KnowledgePlex by members of the target audience. Fannie Mae Foundation\'s leadership team has continued to build upon the findings and recommendations of the Audience Discovery project. The findings have informed additional knowledge-sharing programs and Fannie Mae Foundation’s strategic planning to ensure efforts are rightly aligned with the organization\'s mission and the needs of those in the affordable housing and community development field.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n			<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_E\">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td>\r\n						<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td>\r\n									<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Services</b></td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n												<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\">\r\n													<tbody>\r\n														<tr>\r\n															<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n															<td>Product Assessment &amp; Strategy</td>\r\n														</tr>\r\n														<tr>\r\n															<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n															<td>User Research and Audience Profiling</td>\r\n														</tr>\r\n														<tr>\r\n															<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n															<td>Persona Development</td>\r\n														</tr>\r\n													</tbody>\r\n												</table>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','project',0,27,27,'und',0,'<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_C\" width=\"100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"textheader01\">How visual requirements, task modeling and interface design create user-friendly systems for improved performance and increased ROI. </span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">Overview</span><br />\r\n			Sprint (formerly Nextel Communications) is a leading provider of wireless communications services over an all-digital wireless network serving millions of customers across the United States and around the world.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"center\">\r\n			<table>\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><img src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/cs03_image.gif\" /></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Challenge</span><br />\r\n			Sprint needed to improve the processes and systems it used to acquire, manage and monitor spectrum for the company\'s cellular networks. This was necessary to maintain a high level of service for existing customers, while growing its subscriber base and extending its service offerings. Experience by Design worked with Sprint\'s Corporate Strategy team to identify functionality and features, define critical data and information needs, and design the look and feel of the user interfaces for a suite of integrated desktop and web-based applications to support its spectrum acquisition and network optimization operations.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Solution</span><br />\r\n			Experience by Design brought its Visual Centered Analysis and Modeling™ methodology to work with project stakeholders and team members across the company involved in strategy, spectrum acquisition and network management. Analysis of business and work processes were leveraged to develop system and experience models, application flow diagrams, wireframes and other work products to document findings and designs. These documents were used to guide the planning, design and implementation of the software Sprint needed to achieve its goals.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span class=\"textheader01\">The Result</span><br />\r\n			<span class=\"text01\">Experience by Design delivered design documents specifying the Sprint Corporate Strategy team\'s vision for the software tools they need to successfully meet their operational and strategic goals. The result is a successful and on time implementation of tools that help users perform tasks more efficiently and with greater accuracy. </span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_E\" width=\"\">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td>\r\n						<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Services</b></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n									<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"100%\">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Business and Requirements Analysis</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Concept Modeling and Task Analysis</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Information Architecture &amp; Navigation Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Interaction and User Interface Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p class=\"text01\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','project',0,28,28,'und',0,'<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_C\" width=\"100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\"><span class=\"textheader01\">Web site refresh and redesign for increased sales. </span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p><span class=\"textheader01\">Overview</span><br />\r\n			<span class=\"text01\">Enumerate is a software company whose products and services simplify the process of posting, maintaining, presenting and analyzing numerical data online. </span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"center\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n			<table>\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><img src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/cs01_image.gif\" /></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><span class=\"textheader01\">The Challenge</span><br />\r\n			<span class=\"text01\">Enumerate\'s executive team wanted to transition the organization from a product-focused company to a solutions-oriented company. They needed a firm to rework the content on their corporate web site to reflect the company’s new direction and to support sales and marketing efforts. Experience by Design was hired to develop a design and messaging strategy for the corporate web site that reflected the company\'s new direction. </span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Solution</span><br />\r\n			Experience by Design worked closely with Enumerate\'s executive team to develop a vision, strategy and high-level requirements for the web site redesign. Enumerate wanted the web site to be more in line with the company\'s goals, as well as speak directly to the needs of the target audience. Experience by Design leveraged its findings and experience designing user-friendly web sites and content to create strategy and design documents to guide design and development. Documents included an audience profile to identify target users and their needs; experience flows to map user experience with key features of the site; and wireframes and visual design comps detailing screen layout. These documents were used for stakeholder review and approval, and to guide subsequent development work. Once approved, Experience by Design provided the needed project management, content development, art production and HTML and PHP coding services for an on-time and on-budget delivery.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span class=\"textheader01\">The Result</span><br />\r\n			<span class=\"text01\">Enumerate has a well-organized, streamlined web site that is easy to navigate. It presents marketing and technical information about the company\'s products and services in user-friendly and intuitive ways that are aligned with the executive team\'s vision and the sales team\'s needs. </span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n			<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_E\" width=\"\">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td>\r\n						<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Services</b></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n									<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"100%\">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Audience Profiling</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Conceptual Modeling</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Content Strategy</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Interaction and Interface Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Graphic Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Page Templates and Web Site Development</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><img height=\"10\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/spacer.gif\" /></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Technologies</b></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n									<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"\">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>XHTML</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>CSS</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>PHP</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','project',0,29,29,'und',0,'<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_C\" width=\"100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"textheader01\">User experience design supports collaborative development for a more competitive product offering.</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">Overview</span><br />\r\n			Brabeion Software (now a division of EMC Corporation) is a leading provider of risk and compliance management solutions. The company’s products provide private and public-sector clients with a knowledge base and tools for creating, deploying and managing robust security and regulatory compliance programs.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"center\">\r\n			<table>\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><img src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/cs04_image.gif\" /></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Challenge</span><br />\r\n			Brabeion wanted to extend the capabilities and enhance the performance of its products to grow its share in the marketplace. Brabeion’s leadership team decided to redesign the product’s user interface and core feature set and migrate to a new technical infrastructure to improve overall productivity, performance and appeal.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Solution</span><br />\r\n			Experience by Design brought its knowledge of software user interface design and engineering to help Brabeion’s leadership team. Together, we defined requirements and the technical framework for the product’s new front-end architecture. Findings were used to create functional flows, use cases, annotated wireframes and an ASP .NET and CSS framework to document the product’s new user interface. Once completed and approved, Experience by Design supported the transition of the project to an offshore team to build.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p class=\"text01\"><span class=\"textheader01\">The Result</span><br />\r\n			Brabeion Software now has a best-of-breed product that satisfies even the most complex needs in the enterprise risk and compliance marketplace. With a user-friendly interface, features that make the product more intuitive, along with a more robust technology platform that is flexible and easy to maintain, Brabeion’s customers can now design, deploy and manage security and regulatory compliance programs in less time, with greater precision and at lower costs.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"box_body_E\" width=\"\">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td>\r\n						<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n							<tbody>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Services</b></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n									<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"100%\">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Conceptual Modeling</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Requirements and Use Case Development</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Interaction Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>User Interface Design</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>Front-end Engineering and Development</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><img height=\"10\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/experiatheme/images/spacer.gif\" /></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td colspan=\"2\"><b>Technologies</b></td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n								<tr>\r\n									<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n									<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"\">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>XHTML</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>CSS</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">»</td>\r\n												<td>ASP .NET</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									</td>\r\n								</tr>\r\n							</tbody>\r\n						</table>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n','','full_html');
