INSERT INTO `search_dataset` VALUES (1,'node',' about us experience by design helps you   work more efficiently and reduce time to market lower development costs by defining clear requirements that are accessible to all stakeholders rightly aligned and focus attention on the salient issues communicate more effectively with your audience to increase sales adoption and retention while reducing costs improve ease of use and relevancy and increase customer service and satisfaction while strengthening brand perception and loyalty our focus on user experience provides the clarity and insight that allow us to shape your project in unique ways our methodology takes you from discovery to design and into development in a structured and focused way to ensure your project launches on time on strategy and on budget we tailor our services to meet the needs of each engagement without unnecessary overhead see some of the organizations that have benefited from our services over the years  ',0),(2,'node',' services experience by design customizes its services to the needs and realities of your business we can collaborate with your internal project team or work as an external partner to help you deliver a userfriendly web site or software product to market user experience design services  product ideation prototyping user experience modeling task analysis interaction design information architecture navigation design content strategy user interface design information graphic design online strategy and research services  competitive site review competitor analysis product assessment internet new media strategy online community social networking social media strategy audience profiling user research business analysis requirements developmen project and development support services  project program management rfp consulting frontend programming html javascript css ajax web site software development support  tailor our services  ',0),(3,'node',' projects experience by design provides a range of services to corporate association nonprofit and public sector clients looking to offer userfriendly productive and engaging experiences to users via their web sites or software products we offer flexible solutions ranging from onetime consultations to fullscale design and project support this allows us to align our services and tailor our work to your specific needs our project portfolio includes software corporate web sites and intranets online community and ecommerce web sites and industry portals for clients in a range of industry sectors including advocacy banking biotech education financial services government healthcare housing media entertainment network management sports social media software technology telecommunications and wireless a representative list of our project work includes aarp aol american bankers association  association for financial professionals afp  brabeion software a division of emc corporation  bradford networks buildtopia celera dewalt industrial tool company  enumerate fannie mae finra freddie mac genius rocket georgetown university medical center  goalface humane society of the united states  knowledgeplex lockheed martin military officers association of america perfman sabiamed sallie mae  sprint formerly nextel communications  sprint formerly nextel communications teleglobe a division of tata communications us department of transportation us food drug administration verizon visualcv   some the organizations that have benefited from our services  ',0),(4,'node',' methodology experience by design has been designing successful user experiences for over a decade experience by design brings a holistic and proven approach to the planning and design of userfriendly web sites and software products our methodology centers on the guiding principle that business goals and user needs must be understood and carefully balanced for technology to be delivered in engaging meaningful and effective ways together with our services  our approach ensures a project s integrity through the entire development cyclefrom initial discovery on to design and through successful launch how will the project be managed  our methodology provides an approach to planning and designing web sites and software products that balance user needs and a client s business goals and technical capabilities  enlarge image  our methodology is inclusive and accessible to all project stakeholdersbusiness technical and others our approach gets teams from initial discovery to design and development in a focused structured and efficient manner resulting in projects that launch on time on strategy and on budget our methodology consists of the following four 4 phases    discovery   analysis modeling   design specification   development integration ',0),(5,'node',' discovery what are your strategic goals who is your target audience what information and functionality must your web site or software provide to be successful what other factors are likely to influence the success of your web site or software product during discovery we work with your team to answer these and other questions to ensure goals objectives and priorities for the project are defined and rightly aligned before kicking off the analysis and concept modeling phase   ',0),(6,'node',' analysis modeling how will users locate and get to the information they want or need how should content be organized what information should be placed front and center what functionality will be available and where during analysis and modeling we take a closer look at business goals audience needs content assets technology platforms and other factors that influence design decisions using the findings from discovery phase  we work with you in a series of collaborative sessions each intended to facilitate discussion and build consensus as the team works to refine ideas and requirements the results are concept models and mockups that identify how information will be organized and what features and functionality are required to meet user needs and achieve the desired goals all assumptions and requirements from this phase of the project are gathered and documented in the appropriate format eg reports and diagrams for review and approval before the design and specification phase begins  ',0),(7,'node',' design specification what will the site look like how will content display how will the functional and interactive components work concepts created during the analysis and modeling phase are refined into final designs and specifications how information will display on each page and the ways that navigation and interactive features will work are all defined in detail during design and specification the documents created to capture the design and specifications serve as blueprints to guide the visual designers responsible for the look and feel of the user interface as well as the teams performing the build and testing functions during the development and integration phase   ',0),(8,'node',' development integration marshalling the people and resources needed for the build testing and a successful launch is a complex set of tasks our role during development and integration is to ensure the site or software product is built according to plans set during the design and specification phase  we participate in the review useracceptance testing and resolution of issues that emerge during development we work to address these issues in ways that conform to the established design strategy and patterns and help ensure that the potential negative impacts of changes to the user experience are understood and minimized  ',0),(9,'node',' about us header ',0),(10,'node',' services header ',0),(11,'node',' projects header ',0),(12,'node',' methodology header ',0),(13,'node',' contact us header ',0),(22,'node',' web site evaluation how does your web site measure up experience by design can provide an evaluation of your web site to help you gauge the quality of experience it provides to those who visit and use it our site reviews are performed by knowledgeable user experience professionals they provide an objective evaluation of your web site based on a review of key usability and user experience criteria the site review identifies issues that negatively impact your site s performance and use to get started please answer the following indicates required fields what is your web site address wwwyourwebsiteaddresscom what are the main objectives of the site who is your target audience what aspects of your web site best address the site objectives and the needs of your target audience what aspects of your site are you most pleased with what areas do you feel could be improved what sites competitor or otherwise do you like or admire name email company phone title position  ',0),(23,'node',' contact us send us a message by filling in all fields in the form below or by sending an email to contact at experiencebydesign dot com phone 2407521010 address 10319 westlake drive 101 bethesda md 20817 name email subject message  ',0),(24,'node',' association for financial professionals web site unification and redesign building a daily resource for treasury and finance professionals worldwide overview the association for financial professionals afp is a membership organization serving 16000 treasury and finance professionals around the world afp provides members with breaking news economic research and information to keep current in the evolving world of global treasury and finance afp also provides members with professional networking development and training opportunities as well as public policy representation to legislators and industry regulators the challenge afp s leadership team wanted to bring their web site inline with the dynamic and rapidly evolving needs of its members in the global finance industry afp needed a firm to develop a strategy and plan for a web site that could support the organization s strategic plans experience by design was hired to reorganize the web site s content update its look and feel and upgrade features and functionality as needed to make the site timely accessible and inline with afp s goals to increase revenue and serve as a daily resource for finance professionals worldwide the solution experience by design brought a holistic approach to the strategy for the afp web site redesign experience by design worked with afp executives the project team and stakeholders across the organization to define the target audience strategic goals and business priorities driving the redesign experience by design also reviewed the organization s existing web sites content assets strategic plan competitors and technology platforms to inform the strategy and redesign of the of web site s structure look and feel page layout features and functionality including the afp store conference registration and member sign up and renewal deliverables included a site map functional flows wireframes a visual style guide and other work products to inform the design direct development and support testing during the web site implementation the result association for financial professionals has a web site that is well integrated more engaging relevant and aligned to the organization s business and strategic goals as well as the needs of treasury and finance professionals around the world services  audience profiling competitive site analysis concept modeling content strategy information architecture navigation design interaction interface design graphic design frontend engineering and development technologies  css javascript php  ',0),(25,'node',' goalface engaging the global soccer community around the passion of the game strategy and design services for an interactive sports information and online community experience overview goalface  wwwgoalfacecom  is a content rich social media web site for soccer fans professionals and industry stakeholders that make up the global soccer community goalface brings together a mix of web 20 features and content covering 100000 soccer players and teams from 200 professional leagues across europe the americas africa and asia in an engaging easytouse and fun experience the challenge the goalface management team needed a firm to help ideate design and plan a web site with social networking capabilities built around a library of soccer content they wanted a firm with the ability to create a scalable unified information architecture that was also versed in the latest web 20 and social media trends for a web site expected to be 1000000 pages at launch the solution experience by design brought its grounding in information architecture user experience design and knowledge of online community and social media to help the goalface management team document their vision and strategy experience by design worked with the goalface team to create a product roadmap to guide the planning design build and launch of the web site widgets and mobile applications to be released in phases over several years experience by design used the strategy and roadmap as inputs to inform the initial concepts and designs for the first version of the goalface platform work products and deliverables included a site map navigation models experience flows and concept wireframes to iterate and advance the design of the web site s structure features content display core interactions and user interface patterns once approved experience by design developed user interface specifications to guide the teams that built and tested the goalface web site and applications the result goalface has a fully integrated web site along with a strategy and roadmap for an extended suite of content and social media platforms to build out as they work to engage the global soccer community around the passion of the game services  product ideation strategy online community social media strategy information architecture navigation design task analysis interaction design user experience modeling user interface design expert review user testing frontend engineering and development technologies  css javascript php objectivec  ',0),(26,'node',' knowledgeplex audience discovery grew the adoption and use of an industry portal by improving user experience and content relevancy overview knowledgeplex is an online news tools and information resource for the affordable housing and community development field created by fannie mae foundation fannie mae foundation is a nonprofit organization supporting highperformance community organizations and partnering with others to organize make available and direct the resources needed to facilitate its affordable housing and community revitalization mission the challenge knowledgeplex was created to be the centerpiece of the fannie mae foundation s knowledgesharing programs as a platform for the affordable housing and community development field to connect collaborate share and learn fannie mae foundation s leadership team needed a more refined picture of the knowledgeplex target audience to guide the redesign of the site and align it more directly with the goals and needs of the target audience the solution experience by design was hired to research and build a detailed picture of the target audience for knowledgeplex that outlined the web site s audience as well as their goals wants and needs experience by design used its audience discovery methodology to manage the project from inception through delivery project goals were defined through research and working sessions with internal and external stakeholders topics included the makeup capacity goals and needs of the various segments within the affordable housing and community development field experience by design conducted interviews working sessions and focus groups with a representative sample from each of the target segments and delivered findings and recommendations in a series of deliverables that included an audience profile personas for the primary targets and a findings report the re